### Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Get database schema
GET http://localhost:3001/api/schema

### Execute custom query
POST http://localhost:3001/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "SELECT * FROM api.blog LIMIT 5"
}

### List blog posts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/blog?limit=5

### Get single blog post
GET http://localhost:3001/api/blog/1

### List experience entries
GET http://localhost:3001/api/experience?limit=5

### Get single experience entry
GET http://localhost:3001/api/experience/1

### List users
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users

### AI Chat endpoint
POST http://localhost:3001/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What tables are in the database?",
  "includeSchema": true
}

### AI-enhanced data query
POST http://localhost:3001/api/ai/query-data
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show the latest blog posts."
}
